283
00:24:12,050 --> 00:24:16,950
You know, I’m starting to get tired of
us doing all the previews like this.

284
00:24:16,980 --> 00:24:19,210
Once in a while, can’t we
have someone else…

285
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:21,720
Oh? Oh! You’re perfect. All right!

286
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:23,250
Here, you try doing it this time.

287
00:24:28,860 --> 00:24:31,330
Oh! So, that’s how it is!

288
00:24:31,330 --> 00:24:33,860
Wow, this is going to be
an interesting episode!

